data.description: DEEP WATER WITH A DOCK & 3 ACRES!PonPon is Charleston's best kept secret.  This gated, private hideaway offers you the perfect retreat to fish for Red Breast, Catfish, Largemouth Bass & More! This country home offers an airy, sunny, open living space with a custom kitchen, including stainless steel appliances & luxury granite countertops. The home is elevated with two bedrooms, two baths, & an over sized two car garage/workshop underneath.  There are porches, on both the front & back of the home, from which you will enjoy your water views with live oaks galore!  PRTC provides high speed, fiber optic to the house!All information deemed to be true but is the responsibility of the buyer to verify.
